headline: Raymond James upgrades timber REITs on improving lumber market fundamentals
summary: Investing.com -- Raymond James upgraded timber-focused REITs Weyerhaeuser Company (NYSE:WY) and PotlatchDeltic Corp (NASDAQ:PCH) to "outperform" from "market perform" given their discounted valuations and signs of recovery in lumber market fundamentals.
